snippet: In Blairstown, the “Tour de Farm” took riders through a 35-mile trek with stops at four farms and one country market.
abstract: Tammy LaGorce reviews Tour de Farm, combination bicycle tour and culinary event held in Warren County, that takes riders through 5-, 36- or 78-mile trek with stops at farms and country markets (Metropolitan/New Jersey).
lead_paragraph: In Blairstown, the “Tour de Farm” took riders through a 35-mile trek with stops at four farms and one country market.

headline.main: In a Culinary Event on the Road, It’s Bike to Farm to Tent to Food
headline.print_headline: Bike to Farm to Tent to Food
